Welcome to Text Transformer!

Transform your text effortlessly with our simple yet powerful React application. Whether you need to convert text to uppercase or lowercase, we've got you covered. Say goodbye to tedious manual conversions and hello to streamlined text transformation!

Try it!

Placeholder jumbotron

This faded back jumbotron is useful for placeholder content. It's also a great way to add a bit of context to a page or section when no content is available and to encourage visitors to take a specific action.

Full-width jumbotron

This takes the basic jumbotron above and makes its background edge-to-edge with a .container inside to align content. Similar to above, it's been recreated with built-in grid and utility classes.

Basic jumbotron

This is a simple Bootstrap jumbotron that sits within a .container, recreated with built-in utility classes.
